_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/ec74a1a0aaf374940c0d72b29f8bd0a3.avif?t=1764435121\" width=800 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/094ab1d4866dd3194888b7c0d19ee331.poster.avif?t=1764435121\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/094ab1d4866dd3194888b7c0d19ee331.webm?t=1764435121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/094ab1d4866dd3194888b7c0d19ee331.mp4?t=1764435121\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Life here looks perfect: ocean sunsets, VIP guests, parties that never end, and opportunities that open with the right smile… or touch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But soon the glossy surface begins to crack. Behind the cocktails and confidence hides a world of pressure, temptation, and secrets too big to ignore. And beyond the resort gates — an island that breathes mystery and trouble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charm, ambition, and instinct are your tools.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb your way back to the life you want — or build a new one in paradise, one irresistible encounter at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/7a42f37250514fe057855881e9aa1324.poster.avif?t=1764435121\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660/extras/7a42f37250514fe057855881e9aa1324.webm?t=1764435121\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658660